The Woodcliff Middle School will be holding an Applebee’s Pancake Breakfast fundraiser this Sunday, March 6th, 2016 in support of the 2016 Face Off Competition.

Meals include pancakes, sausage, scrambled eggs and a beverage at $10 per person. Breakfast will be served from 8-10am. All proceeds will benefit the Face Off competition, taking place on 3/22/16.

Tickets are available at the door or e-mail lgander@woodcliff-lake.com.

Northvale Applebee’s - 271 Livingston St, Northvale, NJ 07647
